How to Push Docker Image to Docker Hub.

meanaing: Pushing a Docker image means uploading your locally built Docker image from your computer to Docker Hub, which is an online container registry.

STEP 1: pull the disired image from docker hub
        Docker pull php
STEP 2: check the image pulled
        Docker images
STEP 3: tag the image
        Docker tag php mohtbhau777/smaple:v1
STEP 4: check the tag 
        Docker images
STEP 5: push the tag to the docker hub
        Docker push mohtbhau777/smaple:v1
